1. Hotspot
 1.1 Open WinBox and connect to your Mikrotik
 1.2 Copy default.rsc and fetcher.cfg to your device
 1.3 Run in terminal: "/system reset-configuration keep-users=no no-defaults=yes skip-backup=yes run-after-reset=default.rsc"

 After reset, login again and open terminal

 1.4 Run command: "/import fetcher.cfg"

2. Access point
 2.1 Open WinBox and connect to your Mikrotik
 2.2 Copy default_ap.rsc to your device
 2.3 Run in terminal: "/system reset-configuration keep-users=no no-defaults=yes skip-backup=yes run-after-reset=default_ap.rsc"
